Description: Alexia Tarabotti, who has no soul and can negate supernatural powers, finds herself in the middle of a vampire mystery. Can she clear her name?
Title: SOULLESS, VOL. 2
Author: Gail Carriger

Description: In this reimagining of Lewis Carroll's "Alice's Adventures in Wonderland," the Cheshire Cat, disguised as a human named Boris, vies for Alice's affections.
Title: ALICE IN THE COUNTRY OF CLOVER: CHESHIRE CAT WALTZ, VOL. 3
Author: QuinRose

Description: Naruto and his allies battle an army of undead ninjas and an unexpected resurrection throws them all for a loop.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 59
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Kraft Lawrence, a young merchant finds himself with a companion: Holo, the Wolf-God of the harvest.
Title: SPICE AND WOLF, VOL. 7
Author: Isuna Hasekura

Description: Himari is a cat-spirit sworn to protect teenage Yuto.
Title: OMAMORI HIMARI, VOL. 9
Author: Milan Matra

Description: Keitaro Urashima is forced to live with his grandmother after he fails his entrance exams to Tokyo University. His grandmother owns and operate an all-girl dorm. Shenanigans ensue.
Title: LOVE HINA OMNIBUS, VOL. 4
Author: Ken Akamatsu

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife. In this volume, Ichigo chance at a normal life is disrupted.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 50
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: The latest case for Miles involves the death of an executive, but is it a suicide, a murder or the result of an ancient curse? Will justice be served?
Title: MILES EDGEWORTH, ACE ATTORNEY INVESTIGATIONS, VOL. 3
Author: Kenji Kuroda

Description: Monkey D. Luffy and his motley crew of would-be pirates search for a legendary treasure called “One Piece.”
Title: ONE PIECE, VOL. 65
Author: Eiichiro Oda

Description: High school misfits unite in "The Neighbors Club" in an attempt to better fit in. Will their classmates ever accept them?
Title: HAGANAI, VOL. 1
Author: Yomi Hirasaka and Itachi
